WordPress.org Plugin Assets
===========================

This directory contains assets for the WordPress.org plugin repository.

Required Files (add before submission):
- banner-772x250.png   - Plugin banner image (standard)
- banner-1544x500.png  - Plugin banner image (high-res/retina)
- icon-128x128.png     - Plugin icon (standard)
- icon-256x256.png     - Plugin icon (high-res/retina)

Optional Files:
- screenshot-1.png     - Settings page
- screenshot-2.png     - Order sync status
- screenshot-3.png     - Product linking
- screenshot-4.png     - Bulk sync interface

Notes:
- Banner should show plugin name and optionally WooCommerce + Zoho logos
- Icon should be the plugin logo/branding
- Screenshots should match those described in readme.txt
